<div class="Parallax GParallax1"><div class="Img Binary"><div class="Caption"><a href="#"><div class="Text">Chimie</div></a></div></div><div class="Body2 Orange">La <b>Chimie</b> est la science de l'étude de la matière et de ses transformations.<br>Le but de ce cours est de vous apprendre la <b>Chimie</b> appliquée aux <b>sciences de l'ingénieur</b>.<br>Produit par <b>Gérard KESSE</b>.<br><br><div class="Content0 GSummary1"><div class="Body0" id="Loader_1530820262574"><div class="Row26">Summary 1</div></div><script>loadSummary1("Loader_1530820262574");</script></div></div></div><br><div class="Content2 GTitle1"><div class="MainBlock2"><div class="Content"><h1 class="Title2 Center" id="pH"><a class="Link3" href="#">pH</a></h1><div class="Body3">Le but de cette section est de vous apprendre à calculer le <span class="GColor1" style="color:lime;">pH</span> d'une solution.<br>Produit par <b>Gérard KESSE</b>.<br><br>Le pH permet de mesurer l'acidité d'une solution.<br><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">Grandeurs</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">$pH\rightarrow$ potentiel hydrogène <br>
$[H_3O^+]\rightarrow$ concentration en ion hydronium $(mol.L^{-1})$</div></div><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">pH</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
pH &amp;=&amp; -\log_{10}{\left[H_3O^+]\right.}
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">Concentration en ion hydronium</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
pH &amp;=&amp; -\log_{10}{[H_3O^+]} \\\\
\log_{10}{[H_3O^+]} &amp;=&amp; -pH \\\\
[H_3O^+] &amp;=&amp; 10^{-pH}
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">Solution neutre</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
pH &amp;=&amp; 7 \\\\
-pH &amp;=&amp; -7 \\\\
10^{-pH} &amp;=&amp; 10^{-7} \\\\
[H_3O^+] &amp;=&amp; 10^{-7}
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">Solution acide</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
pH &amp;&lt;&amp; 7 \\\\
-pH &amp;&gt;&amp; -7 \\\\
10^{-pH} &amp;&gt;&amp; 10^{-7} \\\\
[H_3O^+] &amp;&gt;&amp; 10^{-7}
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">Solution basique</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
pH &amp;&gt;&amp; 7 \\\\
-pH &amp;&lt;&amp; -7 \\\\
10^{-pH} &amp;&lt;&amp; 10^{-7} \\\\
[H_3O^+] &amp;&lt;&amp; 10^{-7}
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br><h3 class="Title8 GTitle3">Échelle de pH</h3><div class="Formula GFormula1"><div class="Formula2">\begin{eqnarray}
pH \in [0\ ;14] \\\\
0 \le pH \le 14
\end{eqnarray}</div></div><br><div class="Img3"><img src="img/pH.png" alt="img/pH.png"></div></div></div></div></div><br>